<div class="container">
<h1>Edit Account Details</h1>
<strong>Here you will enter your basic information that the app needs for baseline tracking.</strong>

<p>The app is designed to be user friendly with minimal interaction. It analyzes your blood sugar trends over time and looks for patterns. <br>
These can be the default patterns or ones set by you. Once the app sees a pattern it starts to look at your sleep and health data. <br>
These are then the insights that are provided to you. If you have good or bad blood sugars, what other than the obvious could be helping you? </p>

 <%= form_with(model: @user, local: true) do |form| %>
  <p>
    <%= form.label :first_name %><br>
    <%= form.text_field :first_name %><br>
    <%= form.label :last_name %><br>
    <%= form.text_field :last_name %>
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= form.label :basal_insulin %><br>
    <%= form.text_area :basal_insulin %><br>
    <%= form.label :bolus_insulin %><br>
    <%= form.text_area :bolus_insulin %> 
  </p>
 
  <p>
    <%= form.submit %>
  </p>
 
<% end %>
 <br>
<%= link_to 'Add a Bolus Dose', new_user_bolus_dose_path(@user) %>
<br>
<%= link_to 'Add a Basal Dose', new_user_basal_dose_path(@user) %>
<br>
<%= link_to 'Back', user_path %>
</div>